DeFi

BNB Chain has one of the most diverse DeFi ecosystems across its layer-1 chain (BNB Smart Chain or BSC) and layer 2 (opBNB). BNB is your gateway to the BNB Chain DeFi ecosystem. Here are some of the most important use cases:

Transaction Fees

BNB is required to pay transaction fees when interacting with the network.

Exploring dApps

Utility token across BNB Chain dApps.

Explore dApps

Earning Through dApps

Earn yield on select BNB Chain projects.

Staking

Earn and help secure the BNB Chain ecosystem.

Stake Your BNB

Liquid Staking

Earn higher APY with Liquid Staking Derivatives like slisBNB and clisBNB, and boost returns by investing in DeFi protocols.

slisBNB

Liquid Restaking

Restake your Liquid Staking Tokens (LSTs) like slisBNB to earn additional yield and receive a Liquid Restaked Token for further investment in DeFi protocols.

slisBNB

Decentralized Exchange Fees

CeFi

While DeFi focuses on decentralized services, BNB also plays a critical role in Centralized Finance (CeFi).

Trading Fee Discounts

Discounted trading fees on Binance and can qualify for the VIP program with higher balances for additional perks.

Exclusive Token Sales

Participate in early-stage blockchain projects and new token launches.

Liquidity and Lending

Earn yield by pooling tokens with Binance Liquid Swap or lend them through Binance Launchpool to support new projects and earn rewards.

BNB Vault

BNB Vault is a yield aggregator that lets users stake BNB in various Binance products, including Simple Earn and Launchpool, for streamlined rewards across the ecosystem.

Promotions

BNB, slisBNB and clisBNB holders are all eligible for Binance Launchpool, Megadrop, HODLer Airdrop.

Learn more on Binance.com

PayFi

PayFi, or Payment Finance, is where blockchain technology integrates into real-world payment solutions, offering real-time settlement for transactions. BNB is a key enabler of PayFi use cases, facilitating secure, fast, and cost-effective transactions.

Shopping and Spending

Binance Pay allows users to shop online using BNB and pay for goods and services on e-commerce platforms.

Travel

Book airfare and accommodation from a range of providers like Travala.com

Entertainment

Participate in games and activities hosted by Binance and earn BNB rewards.

Services

Pay for real-world and digital services.

Financial Services

Loan, trade, invest, and pay for expenses.

BNB Burn

How does it work?

BNB adopts an Auto-Burn system to reduce its total supply to 100,000,000 BNB. This mechanism adjusts the burn amount based on BNB's price and the number of blocks on BNB Smart Chain (BSC), ensuring transparency and predictability.

BNB Reimbursement

The BNB Pioneer Burn Program reimburses lost coins and counts them towards the official burn count.

Gas Fee Aspect

BNB utilizes a real-time burning mechanism tied to gas fees. A fixed ratio of collected gas fees is burned in each block, determined by BSC validators.
